<span class="token comment"># Update</span>
pm2 update
</code></pre> <div class="line-numbers-wrapper"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br></div></div><h2 id="cluster"><a href="#cluster" class="header-anchor">#</a> Cluster</h2> <div class="language-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-sh"><code>// cluster: n <span class="token punctuation">(</span>n개<span class="token punctuation">)</span>, -n <span class="token punctuation">(</span>core 수 - n개<span class="token punctuation">)</span>
